snippet.title: The Magic Book - Amit Bhadana - Sci-Fi Comedy ( Katayi Zeher )
snippet.description:
Kuch logon ki bad luck hi kharaab hoti hai. Lekin jab kismet hoti hai meharbaan to gadha bhi ban jata hai pehelwaan. Aise hi ek din bade bade spane dekhne wale Amit ke hath lag jati hai ek karamati kitaab. Kitaab  ka naam Katayi Zeher aur kaam bhi Katai Zeher. Lekin kya Amit sambhal payega is magic book ko? Ye to hai lakh rupay ka sawaal. To dekhiye aur doston aur family ko bhi dikhaiye ye jadu bhara, dhamakedaar video.

snippet.title: The 20 Million Journey | Dedicated To All My Fans | Ashish Chanchlani & Team
snippet.description:
Kaise ho sab log?
Ye dekho maine hafte pehle ye video edit ki
Jab main iss video ko edit kar raha tha i got way too emotional
I had tears when this finished.
I cannot believe this hum sabko saath mein 6 saal ho gaye?
From being an engineering student to a “celebrity”? Celebrity shayad bann toh gaye lekin dil mein ab bhi wohi college student waali feeling aati hai
This is something i never imagined
Aur 2 CRORE SUBSCRIBERS? Mazak chal raha hai kya😂😂 muje toh bas 100k karne the
Kaha pahucha diya bhai?
Who would have thought?
Ye video, ye journey, ye puri life main aap sab fans ko dedicate karta hu
I think one of the major reasons you all connect to me and show so much of love is because you see yourself in me
Which is absolutely true
I am one of you, my videos are based on you all, and nothing in my life gives me more happiness than seeing you all laugh and enjoy our work
Main aur meri puri team ACV ki taraf se ye video ek bahut bada thank you hai aap logo ko
3 mahine ke lambe dark depressing time ke baad ab jaake dil dimaag mein jaan aayi hai all THANKS TO YOU.
Aap ye 100 baar sun chuke ho ki how much you all mean to us but i’ll still say this again
YOU ALL MEAN THE MOST TO US
WE LOVE YOU.
Thank you for giving this ordinary boy and extraordinary career to live.
Comment a special memory you have with me or my videos❤️🙏🥺
I wanna thank some major people in my life journey : My parents, Muskan, Karishma Bhatia, Kunal chhabhria, Akash Dodeja, Simran Dhanwani, Jashan Sirwani, Tanish Sirwani, Anmol Sachar, Rohit Sadhwani, Ritesh Sadhwani, Grishim Nawani, Aditya Chanchlani, Suhan Chanchlani,Minesh Santani, Jacky Chawla, Karan gidwani, Prithvi Nathani, Sid Kedare, Deepak Sampat, Akshata sonawane, Akash Jagtap, Yogesh Makhija, Raaj Raisinghani & Navjyot Chandnani.
Sorry if i missed someone 
LOTS OF LOVE ACVIANS
#AshishChanchlani #20Million #Acvians

snippet.description:

Click to watch all the Weekly Reliv episodes: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7aq_DUPLxBkU49WEPPcecgS

Weekly ReLIV is a special compilation of the week’s episodes and is created to give the viewer a feel of the show’s story and it’s high points. The weekly ReLIV here is created especially for the viewers who have missed the week’s episodes and would like to catch up on the plot of their favorite shows. Watch the Weekly ReLIV of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah of the episodes from 11th November To 15th November 2019.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

snippet.title: Darr Ke Aage Jeet Hai #JeetengePhirSe | Mountain Dew| Sukhwinder Singh |Yeh Desh Hai Veer Jawaano Ka
snippet.description:
It’s not just a song. It’s a salute by Mountain Dew to India’s legendary legacy of winning in the face of fear - desh ki sadiyon se reet hai, darr ke aage jeet hai.
Through the iconic ‘Ye Desh Hai Veer Jawaano Ka’ reimagined, it’s a timely reminder that we, as a nation, have beaten the odds over and over. And if we could do it in the past, we can do it again. 
#JeetengePhirSe

Singer: Sukhwinder Singh
Music composed by: Ram Sampath
Lyrics: Swanand Kirkire
Directed by: Bharat Bala

Original Singers: Mohammed Rafi, Balbir
Original Music Director: O.P. Nayyar
Original Lyricist: Sahir Ludhianvi 

Follow Mountain Dew on:

YouTube
https://www.youtube.com/user/MountainDewIndia

Instagram
https://instagram.com/mountaindewin

Also hear on:
https://ampl.ink/prx8G
Wynk: https://bit.ly/DarrKeAageWynk 
Resso: https://bit.ly/DarrKeAageResso

Ye Desh Hai Veer Jawaanon Ka, Albelon Ka, Mastaanon Ka
Is Desh Ka Yaaron Kya Kahna, Ye Desh Hai Duniya Ka Gehna

Ye Yoddhaon Ki Bhoomi Hai Ham Befikar Chalein
Saugandh Liye Is Maati Ki Hoke Nidarr Chalein
 
Nas-Nas Mein Gholta Jazba Hai Dil Mein Ye Geet Hai
Ke Darr Ke Aage, Darr Ke Aage, Darr Ke Aage Jeet Hai
 
Ye Desh Hai Veer Jawaanon Ka, Albleon Ka, Mastaanon Ka
Yahan Sadiyon Se Ye Reet Hai Ji, Har Darr Ke Aage Jeet Hai Ji

Chalda harek nal Corra ve jattan,
Hass k dikha de kade bhora ve jattan,
Hale ta lagi nu ek saal  nhi hoyea,
 kivein Zindagi langhuni lgaaa jahoran v jattan,
koi hor ta nhi Kutt k khawaundi churiyan,
Mere kolo Rakh dain  bna k duriyan, 
Rab ne shakal deti eni sohni tenu, 
Ve Rakh da mathe te Tu PA k tiudiyan,
changiyan nhi eh Gallan changiyan nhi,
Mere nal Karda Tu jehriyan,

Teri ta limit bus fun tak ve, 
Dardi rehndi aa Banda mar na dai,
Teri ta thinking bus gun tak ve, 
velly sire de Sare Yaar ne tere, 
Dil de karib 3-4 ne tere, Mere nalo time vadh kadh da jinha lyi,
aakhri te pehla jihre payar ne tere, 
mere vang fikar jatauna nhi kise ne,
Mil Jan giya tenu ve Bathriyan, 
jina Tu adhab.......2.

Aaki payi aa "Jashan Jagdev"tere to,
jhuthiyan trifa hundiyan mere ton, 
sabar sukar nam Di chij koi ptaa nhi tenu, Vekheya jadon  da ve mein ho ke nehre ton, 
kala mall kha k aakh Laal rakhda, 
ki bol k dasan ve jo Tu haal krdain,
pi k Ghar Di kadhi ve nitt ladh k  Sona ee, 
Tu ta bhul v Jana ee,  Tu Kamal krdain,  
russi nu manaun lyi ki launa eh schema,
Gappan valiya leyona ee haneriyan, 
Jina Tu adhab ..........2

snippet.description:
വണ്ടിപ്രേമികൾ ഏറെ ആകാംക്ഷയോടെ കാത്തിരുന്ന മഹീന്ദ്രയുടെ പുതുപുത്തൻ Thar 2020 യുടെ ഒരു ടെസ്റ്റ് ഡ്രൈവ് & യൂസർ എക്സ്പീരിയൻസ് ഷെയറിംഗ് ആണ് ഈ വീഡിയോ. വണ്ടിയെക്കുറിച്ചുള്ള നിങ്ങളുടെ അഭിപ്രായങ്ങൾ കമന്റ് ചെയ്യുക. #techtraveleat #mahindrathar

Mahindra Thar 2020 Test Drive - First Impressions & User Experience by Tech Travel Eat with @Abhijith Bhakthan 

The All-New Mahindra Thar is a 4 & 6 seater SUV. Know more about the Thar's models, specs, features, mileage, colours, variants, interior & exterior. The Thar 2020 is available with a choice of two engine options: a 150PS 2.0-litre turbo petrol and a 130PS 2.2-litre diesel. Both engines can be had with a 6-speed manual or a 6-speed automatic transmission. 4x4 is offered as standard. Mahindra Thar 2020 variants include AX, AX (O) and LX.

snippet.title: Akon & Vlad Get into Heated Debate Over Akon Doing 'Locked Up 2' with Tekashi (Part 7)
snippet.description:
Part 6: https://youtu.be/5u4oO-LT6Aw
Part 1: https://youtu.be/G7u1ND_33MY
--------
In this clip, Akon talked about his hit single "Locked Up" not being a favorite of the label. He said that the entire budget was geared toward his other song, "Belly Dancer," and was only given $10,000 to promote "Locked Up." Akon detailed how a mini prison tour grew out of the tight budget. 
Later, Akon and Vlad discussed Akon's collaboration with Tekashi 6ix9ine and why that upset Vlad.

snippet.title: Introducing Fudgy the Golden Retriever Puppy
snippet.description:
Everyone, say hello to Fudgy!  He's a Golden Retriever puppy, and he loves chewing on socks, sleeves, strings, chom choms, shoes, and just about everything else really.  He's a really clever boy as well, and has learned how to sit, give paw, and he's taking to his crate quite well!  

If you haven't seen our announcement yet, we've moved back to Canada now.  It’s been a very busy three months for us, as we transitioned back into living in Canada.  We’ve both been taking time off of YouTube to think about what kind of content we want to make in the future.  Do we still want to vlog?  Do we still want to talk about food and travel?  

We’re not too sure, and especially with our move back to Canada, where we can be closer to family and friends, we haven’t had much time to be as creative as we usually are.  Our focus first and foremost is taking care of our wellbeing, which we’ve been neglecting for a long time.  We have more support here and more options.  

And so, while we explore those options, and figure out what our next steps in life are, allow me to introduce you to the newest member of the Stawski family: Fudgy, the very sweet golden retriever puppy.  He’s been a huge help for me (Simon here) during this time, and I hope some of his cuteness brightens your day the way he’s brightened mine.

I’d like to just post some videos of Fudgy being cute and silly for a while.  I’ll be sharing some pics of him too, because I’m a fawning father alright?  He’s just so adorable ❤️

#goldenretriever #puppy #omgheissocuteamiright?

snippet.title: UFC 252 Highlights | Miocic retains heavyweight title with decisive win over Cormier | CBS Sports HQ
snippet.description:
The third fight in classic fight trilogies doesn't always live up to the lofty expectations set by the two previous meetings. In the case of UFC heavyweight champion Stipe Miocic's rubber match with Daniel Cormier at UFC 252, however, the third meeting surpassed anything that happened in the first two bouts as Miocic managed to outwork Cormier over five rounds for a unanimous decision victory in a thrilling battle.

The hype train of rising bantamweight "Sugar" Sean O'Malley took a detour on its trip toward crossover stardom after an apparent leg injury led to an opportunistic finish from Marlon "Chito" Vera on Saturday.

The first round and a half of the UFC 252 heavyweight clash between Jairzinho Rozenstruik and Junior dos Santos belonged to dos Santos, but Rozenstruik proved once again that it only takes one of his shots to turn a fight, scoring a TKO in the second round to rebound from a devastating loss in his last outing.

snippet.title: Sean O'Malley Devastating Foot Injury at UFC 252 - Doctor Explains What Happened!
snippet.description:
'Suga' Sean O'Malley lost to Marlon 'Chito' Vera at UFC 252 ending the Suga Show's unbeaten streak in the UFC. A major reason for O'Malley's defeat was the foot injury he sustained during the fight. He had a prior LisFranc injury a couple of years ago requiring surgery, and the concern from Sean O'Malley is that this is the same injury. In this video Dr. Brian Sutterer will review the injury footage and anatomy to explain how this devastating injury occurred.

snippet.title: We've Moved To Canada
snippet.description:
Yup, that's right. We’ve moved back to Canada!  

Sorry for the worry we might have caused you all, but I’m sure you can understand that it was an extremely tough decision to make. We took time off from social media and from posting videos to really think about what we were going to do. To get these changes in motion.  

We were both concerned about the well being of our families during this time. As for me (Martina), since my dad passed away, I was especially worried about my mom being isolated and alone due to the necessary social distancing.  My plan is to spend more time with her, maybe even learn some recipes that I can share with you all for Martina’s Midnight Munchies!

Simon has taken a step back from being on camera and he has gotten back into writing, something he truly loved doing while in university.  He’s working on a book and has even been contemplating enrolling back into school. But currently he's been a bit busy with... well, you’ll see in the next video 😉 

Majority of us have had to make massive changes during this time period.  Covid has changed the way of the world, so we’re going to have to change with it.  

I’ve always enjoyed making videos, editing, creating music, doodling so I’d like to keep sharing whatever ideas come out of my crazy head. Of course, I've also got some Build A Ladder segments I've been planning, so I'm going to give myself a smaller work load but try to be more consistent. We'll see if I can stick to my personal goals. Simon too is also going to focus on the creative ideas and processes that he enjoys, so we're looking to more flexible.

It’ll be a change, but we’ve dealt with change before. Hopefully some of you will stick around and will enjoy the new changes 2020 will bring to our channel.

MORE ABOUT ANNABELLE THE DOLL 
Annabelle is an allegedly haunted doll housed in the occult museum of the paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren. A character based on the doll is a reoccurring antagonist in the Conjuring Universe.
Background

According to the Warrens, a student nurse was given the doll in 1970. They say the doll behaved strangely, and that a psychic medium told the student that the doll was inhabited by the spirit of a deceased girl named "Annabelle". The student and her roommate tried to accept and nurture the spirit-possessed doll, but the doll reportedly exhibited malicious and frightening behavior. It was at this point that the Warrens say they were first contacted, moving the doll to their museum after pronouncing it demonically possessed.  The doll remains in a glass box at The Warrens' Occult Museum in Monroe, Connecticut. 

Texas State University assistant professor of religious studies Joseph Laycock says most skeptics have dismissed the Warren's museum as "full of off-the-shelf Halloween junk, dolls and toys, books you could buy at any bookstore". Laycock calls the Annabelle legend an "interesting case study in the relationship between pop culture and paranormal folklore" and speculates that the demonic doll trope popularized by films such as Child's Play, Dolly Dearest, and The Conjuring likely emerged from early legends surrounding Robert the Doll as well as a Twilight Zone season 5 episode 6 titled "Living Doll" (in which the character of the mother is coincidentally named Annabelle), released 5 years prior to the Warren's story. Laycock suggests that "the idea of demonically-possessed dolls allows modern demonologists to find supernatural evil in the most banal and domestic of places."

snippet.title: Meet Rampart – Apex Legends Character Trailer
snippet.description:
The best modder in the Outlands, Rampart backs up her big mouth with big guns she designed herself. http://x.ea.com/63058

When one door burns to the ground, another opens. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh lost her shop, but she gained an invite to the Apex Games. She may not have set out to become a Legend, but now that she’s here, she’s excited to show the world what Sheila can do. 


Rampart can’t go home, so she’s going big -- her natural affinity for LMGs allows her to shoot more and reload faster. She can drop a high-tech cover to block incoming shots and joice up her team’s fire. And when you really need to call in the big guns, her Ultimate does just that. When you meet Sheila, you better hope she’s on your side.

Ready to dance?

Learn more about Rampart’s story: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M9Pmf9AB4Mo

localizations.ko.title: 램파트 소개 – Apex 레전드 캐릭터 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
아웃랜드의 최고 제조의 달인인 램파트는 과장된 표현을 좋아합니다. 그리고 그 표현을 자신이 직접 디자인한 커다란 총을 들고 증명해내죠. http://x.ea.com/63058

문이 닫히면 어딘가 창문이 열리기 마련입니다. 람야 ""램파트"" 파레크는 자신의 가게를 잃었지만, Apex 게임의 초대장을 받았습니다. 램파트는 처음부터 레전드가 되기로 마음먹은 건 아니지만, Apex 게임에 도착한 이상 쉴라의 파괴적인 능력을 세상에 보여주려 합니다. 


돌아갈 집이 없는 램파트는 오히려 대담한 도전장을 던집니다. 램파트는 LMG를 능숙하게 다루어 더 많이 쏘고 더 빠르게 재장전을 합니다. 최첨단 엄폐물을 배치하여 들어오는 총격을 막고 팀의 총격을 강화합니다. 그러다 정말로 큰 총을 불러야 할 때가 온다면, 그녀는 얼티밋 스킬을 꺼내듭니다. 쉴라를 만나게 된다면, 반드시 램파트가 팀에 있길 바랍니다.

함께 춤추실 준비 되셨습니까?

램파트의 이야기에 대해 더 알아보기: [link]

localizations.sv.title: Möt Rampart - Apex Legends-karaktärstrailer
localizations.sv.description:
Rampart är den bästa moddaren i Outlands och hon blandar mycket snack och mycket verkstad tack vare vapnen hon själv har designat. http://x.ea.com/63058

När en dörr brinner ner till grunden öppnas en annan. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh förlorade sin butik, men hon fick en inbjudan till Apex Games. Hon siktade kanske inte på att bli en legend, men nu när hon är här ser hon fram emot att visa världen vad Sheila går för.


Rampart kan inte gå hem, så hon går all-in --  hennes naturliga förkärlek för LMG låter henne skjuta mer och ladda om snabbare. Hon kan ta fram ett högteknologiskt skydd som blockerar inkommande skott och sätter piff på sitt lags ammunition. Och när det verkligen blir dags för det tunga artilleriet, så kan du förvänta dig just det från hennes Ultimate. När du träffar Sheila får du hoppas att hon är på din sida.

Redo att dansa?

localizations.it.title: Rampart – Apex Legends - Il trailer
localizations.it.description:
Rampart è la regina della tecnologia nelle Terre Straniere. Grazie alle armi da fuoco che progetta e costruisce, non ha paura di mostrare ai nemici di che pasta è fatta. http://x.ea.com/63058

Quando si chiude una porta, si apre un portone. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh ha perso il suo negozio, ma ha ricevuto un invito per gli Apex Games. Non avrebbe mai creduto che un giorno sarebbe diventata una leggenda, ma ora è impaziente di mettersi al lavoro e mostrare al mondo intero di cosa è capace Sheila. 


Rampart non può tornare a casa, perciò è pronta a dare il massimo nell'arena. Il suo talento naturale con le LMG le consente di sparare più a lungo e ricaricare più rapidamente. Inoltre, può posizionare una copertura hi-tech che blocca i colpi in arrivo e potenzia quelli in uscita. La sua mitragliatrice, poi, è perfetta per affrontare le situazioni più difficili in battaglia. Quando incontrerai Sheila, spera che sia dalla tua parte.

Preparati a entrare in pista!

localizations.no.title: Møt Rampart – Apex Legends-karaktertrailer
localizations.no.description:
Den beste modderen i randen, Rampart, forsvarer den store kjeften sin med de store våpnene hun selv har utviklet. http://x.ea.com/63058

Når én dør blir til aske, er det en annen som åpnes. Ramya «Rampart» Parekh mistet verkstedet sitt, men hun fikk en invitasjon til Apex-lekene. Hun hadde kanskje ingen planer om å bli til en legende, men nå er hun her og hun gleder seg til å vise verden hva Sheila kan gjøre. 


Rampart kan ikke dra hjem, så da retter hun kursen mot seier – hennes naturlige preferanse for LMG-er lar henne skyte mer og lade om raskere. Hun kan sette ut et avansert skydd som blokkerer skudd fra fienden og piffer opp ildkraften til laget sitt. Og når situasjonen virkelig krever kraftigere skytevåpen, så fikser ultimaten hennes akkurat det. Når du endelig får hilse på Sheila bør du håpe på at hun er på din side.

localizations.ru.title: Встречайте Рампарт — трейлер персонажа Apex Legends
localizations.ru.description:
За хвастовством Рампарт, автора лучших модификаций во Внешних землях, стоят здоровенные пушки, конструкцию которых она продумала сама. http://x.ea.com/63058

Когда одна дверь сгорает дотла, открывается другая. Рамья «Рампарт» Парекх лишилась магазина, но обрела приглашение на Игры Apex. Может, она и не планировала становиться легендой, но раз уж она здесь, то с радостью продемонстрирует всему миру, на что способна Шейла. 


У Рампарт нет пути назад, поэтому она гордо шагает вперед с пушкой наперевес. Благодаря своей тяге к ручным пулеметам она может перезаряжать их быстрее и делать больше выстрелов. Ее примочки обеспечивают отряду надежное укрытие, которое блокирует огонь снаружи и усиливает стрельбу команды. Если же нужно пустить в ход тяжелую артиллерию, ее спецумение придется весьма кстати. Повстречаетесь с Шейлой — надейтесь, что она на вашей стороне.

localizations.es-MX.description:
Rampart es la mejor modificadora de las tierras desconocidas y, aunque habla demasiado, respalda sus palabras con grandes armas que diseñó ella misma. http://x.ea.com/63058

Cuando se quema una puerta, otra se abre. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh perdió su tienda, pero ganó una invitación a los Apex Games. Quizás nunca buscó ser una leyenda, pero ahora que está aquí, podrá mostrarle al mundo lo que Sheila puede hacer. 


Rampart no puede regresar a casa, así que irá con todo: su afinidad natural por las ametralladoras ligeras le permite disparar más y recargar más rápido. Puede desplegar coberturas de alta tecnología para bloquear los disparos enemigos y amplificar los de su equipo. Y cuando realmente necesites un peso pesado, su habilidad definitiva es lo que buscas. localizations.fr-FR.title: Découvrez Rampart - Trailer personnage Apex Legends
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Meilleure experte en modding des Terres Sauvages, Rampart a le verbe haut et le canon - qu’elle a souvent conçu elle-même - à portée de main. http://x.ea.com/63058

Quand une porte brûle, une autre s’ouvre. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh a perdu sa boutique, mais elle a gagné une invitation aux Jeux Apex. Rampart n’était pas programmée pour devenir une Légende mais, maintenant qu’elle est dans la place, elle compte bien montrer de quoi Sheila est capable. 


Rampart ne peut pas rentrer chez elle, alors autant sortir le grand jeu : son attirance naturelle pour les mitrailleuses lui confère une cadence de tir élevée et un rechargement rapide. Elle a aussi recours à une couverture technologique qui bloque les tirs ennemis et amplifie ceux de son équipe. Et, pour ce qui est d‘envoyer du lourd, sa capacité ultime fait largement le boulot : si vous croisez Sheila, priez pour être dans son camp !

Vous êtes prêts à danser ?

localizations.pl.description:
Rampart to najlepsza moderka na Odludziu. Jest wyszczekana i ma własnoręcznie zaprojektowane potężne spluwy. http://x.ea.com/63058

Gdy jedne drzwi spłoną, otworzą się następne. Ramya „Rampart” Parekh straciła swój sklep, ale otrzymała zaproszenie do Igrzysk Apex. Może i nie miała w planach zostać legendą, ale gdy już się tu znalazła, z radością pokaże światu, co potrafi jej Sheila. 


Rampart nie może wrócić do domu, więc idzie na całego – jej naturalna ciągota do LKM-ów sprawia, że jest bardziej wydajną strzelczynią oraz szybko przeładowuje bronie. Potrafi postawić zaawansowaną technologicznie osłonę blokującą nadlatujące pociski i zmotywować swoją drużynę. I kiedy naprawdę chcesz wytoczyć najcięższe działa, jej zdolność specjalna zrealizuje to w pełni. Gdy spotkasz Sheilę, módl się, żeby była po twojej stronie.

Gotowi do tańca?

Więcej o historii Rampart dowiecie się tutaj: [link].

localizations.ja.description:
アウトランズ随一のモッダーであるランパートは、自ら設計したビッグな銃でビッグマウスを体現してみせる。http://x.ea.com/63058

ドアが1枚焼け落ちれば、また1枚が開く。ラミャ・“ランパート”・パレクは店を失ったが、Apexゲームへの招待状を掴んだ。レジェンドを目指すつもりはないかもしれないが、やって来たからにはシェイラの力量を世界に知らしめようと心躍らせている。


帰る家がないランパートは大胆に行く。LMGとの相性が良いため、弾数が多く、リロードが高速。ハイテクカバーで銃撃を受け止め、チームの火力を上げる。ビッグガンが必要になったときには、「アルティメット」の出番である。シェイラと会うときには、彼女が味方であることを願おう。

localizations.pt-BR.description:
A melhor modder das Terras Ermas, Rampart nunca para de falar, mas está sempre bem armada. http://x.ea.com/63058

Quando uma porta pega fogo e vira cinzas, outra se abre. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh perdeu a oficina que tinha, mas ganhou um convite para os Jogos Apex. Ela não desejava se tornar uma Lenda, mas agora que está aqui, ela quer mostrar para o mundo o que Sheila pode fazer. 


Rampart veio pra ficar, então ela aposta tudo na afinidade natural com metralhadoras leves, permitindo que dispare mais e recarregue mais rápido. Ela pode posicionar uma cobertura de alta tecnologia que bloqueia disparos inimigos e amplifica disparos aliados. E quando precisar de armamento pesado, a Suprema dela cumpre bem o serviço. Quando conhecer Sheila, torça para ela estar do seu lado.

localizations.da.description:
Rampart en en rapkæftet modder fra Outlands, der selv designer sine egne våben. http://x.ea.com/63058

Når en dør går op i flammer, er det altid et vindue, der åbner sig. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh mistede sin butik, men til gengæld fik hun en invitation til Apex Games. Det var ikke hendes mål at blive en legende, men nu hvor hun er med i kampen, glæder hun sig til at vise, hvad Sheila kan. 


Rampart går ikke stille med dørene – hun har smag for maskingeværer og kan skyde og lade hurtigt. Hun kan smide en højteknologisk dækning, der beskytter hende mod fjendens skud, samtidig med at den forstærker hendes holdkammeraters skud. Og når du virkelig har brug for det tunge skyts, er hendes ultimate det perfekte valg. Når du ser Sheila, håber du straks, at hun er på dit hold.

Er du klar til at danse?

localizations.de-DE.description:
Als beste Modderin der Outlands lässt Rampart ihren großen Sprüchen ebenso große Waffen folgen, die sie selbst entworfen hat. http://x.ea.com/63058

Wenn eine Tür niedergebrannt wird, öffnet sich eine andere. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh hat ihren Laden verloren, aber eine Einladung zu den Apex-Spielen erhalten. Sie hatte zwar nie vor, eine Legende zu werden, aber wo sie schon mal hier ist, freut sie sich darauf, der ganzen Welt zu zeigen, was Sheila kann. 


Da Rampart nicht nach Hause gehen kann, geht sie aufs Ganze. Dank ihrer Vorliebe für LMGs kann sie länger feuern und schneller nachladen. Außerdem kann sie Beschuss mit einer Hightech-Deckung blocken und die Schüsse ihres Teams verstärken. Und falls sie mal richtig schweres Gerät braucht, greift sie auf ihre ultimative Fähigkeit zurück. Wenn du Sheila triffst, solltest du hoffen, dass sie auf deiner Seite steht.

localizations.pt-PT.description:
A melhor modder das Outlands, Rampart fala demais, mas as armas enormes que cria também são demais.
http://x.ea.com/63058


Quando uma porta se fecha, abre-se uma janela a tiro. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh pode ter perdido a sua oficina, mas ganhou um convite para os Apex Games. Nunca quis ser uma lenda mas, já que está aqui, vai mostrar ao mundo o poder de Sheila. 


Rampart não pode ir para casa, por isso vai dar tudo o que tem. A sua afinidade natural por LMGs dá-lhe uma velocidade de disparo maior e um tempo de recarga mais curto. Pode criar uma cobertura energética para bloquear o fogo inimigo e potenciar os disparos da sua equipa. E, quando precisares de uma arma mesmo grande, o seu Derradeiro não desilude. Quando vires a Sheila, vais rezar para que esteja na tua equipa.

localizations.fi.title: Tutustu Rampartiin – Apex Legends -hahmotraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Outlandsin paras modaaja Rampart seisoo suurten puheidensa takana käyttämällä itse suunnittelemiaan isoja aseita. http://x.ea.com/63058
 
 Kun yksi ovi palaa maan tasalle, toinen avautuu. Ramya ”Rampart” Parekh menetti kauppansa mutta sai kutsun Apex Gamesiin. Hän ei ehkä pyrkinyt legendaksi, mutta nyt, kun hän on täällä, hän on innoissaan päästessään näyttämään maailmalle, mihin Sheila pystyy. 
 
 
 Rampart ei voi mennä kotiin, joten hän pistää kaiken peliin – hänen luonnollinen mieltymyksensä kevyisiin konekivääreihin antaa hänen ampua enemmän ja ladata nopeammin. Hän pystyy pystyttämään huipputeknisen suojan estämään kohti tulevat laukaukset ja tehostamaan ryhmänsä tulitusta. Kun sinun todella pitää saada suuret aseet taisteluun, hänen Ultimatensa tekee juuri sen. Kun tapaat Sheilan, sinun on paras toivoa, että hän on sinun puolellasi.
 
 Oletko valmis tanssiin?
 
 Lue lisää Rampartin tarinasta: [link].

localizations.nl-NL.description:
Rampart, de beste Modder in de Outlands, heeft een grote mond, maar maakt het ook waar met de grote wapens die ze zelf heeft ontworpen. http://x.ea.com/63058

Als één deur tot op de grond afbrandt, gaat er een andere deur open. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh is een winkel armer, maar een uitnodiging voor de Apex Games rijker. Ze was misschien niet van plan om een Legend te worden, maar nu ze hier is, wil ze de wereld graag laten zien wat Sheila kan. 


Rampart kan niet naar huis, dus ze pakt het groots aan: dankzij haar natuurlijke affiniteit voor LMG's kan ze meer schieten en sneller herladen. Ze kan hightech dekking geven om vijandelijke schoten te blokkeren en het vuur van haar team op te peppen. En als je echt grote wapens nodig hebt, doet haar Ultimate precies dat. Als je Sheila ontmoet, kun je maar beter hopen dat ze aan jouw kant staat.

Klaar om te dansen?

身為邊疆最厲害的模組師，蕾帕特雖然口氣不小，但她自己設計的槍枝也不賴。http://x.ea.com/63058

天無絕人之路。拉米雅‧帕里克，綽號「蕾帕特」，失去了她的商店，但她卻受邀參與 Apex 競賽。儘管她從未打算成為一名英雄，但她現在等不及想要讓全世界瞧瞧席拉的厲害


蕾帕特回不了家，所以她決定大幹一場－－她擅長使用輕機槍，這讓她能夠更常射擊並更快地填裝彈藥她能夠部署一道高科技掩護來阻擋來襲攻擊，同時強化隊友的彈藥當你需要使用強大的火力時，交給她的絕招當你見到席拉時，你最好希望它是你的隊友

snippet.title: Akon & Vlad Get into Heated Debate Over Akon Doing 'Locked Up 2' with Tekashi (Part 7)
snippet.description:
Part 6: https://youtu.be/5u4oO-LT6Aw
Part 1: https://youtu.be/G7u1ND_33MY
--------
In this clip, Akon talked about his hit single "Locked Up" not being a favorite of the label. He said that the entire budget was geared toward his other song, "Belly Dancer," and was only given $10,000 to promote "Locked Up." Akon detailed how a mini prison tour grew out of the tight budget. 
Later, Akon and Vlad discussed Akon's collaboration with Tekashi 6ix9ine and why that upset Vlad.

snippet.title: UFC 252 Highlights | Miocic retains heavyweight title with decisive win over Cormier | CBS Sports HQ
snippet.description:
The third fight in classic fight trilogies doesn't always live up to the lofty expectations set by the two previous meetings. In the case of UFC heavyweight champion Stipe Miocic's rubber match with Daniel Cormier at UFC 252, however, the third meeting surpassed anything that happened in the first two bouts as Miocic managed to outwork Cormier over five rounds for a unanimous decision victory in a thrilling battle.

The hype train of rising bantamweight "Sugar" Sean O'Malley took a detour on its trip toward crossover stardom after an apparent leg injury led to an opportunistic finish from Marlon "Chito" Vera on Saturday.

The first round and a half of the UFC 252 heavyweight clash between Jairzinho Rozenstruik and Junior dos Santos belonged to dos Santos, but Rozenstruik proved once again that it only takes one of his shots to turn a fight, scoring a TKO in the second round to rebound from a devastating loss in his last outing.

snippet.title: Introducing Fudgy the Golden Retriever Puppy
snippet.description:
Everyone, say hello to Fudgy!  He's a Golden Retriever puppy, and he loves chewing on socks, sleeves, strings, chom choms, shoes, and just about everything else really.  He's a really clever boy as well, and has learned how to sit, give paw, and he's taking to his crate quite well!  

If you haven't seen our announcement yet, we've moved back to Canada now.  It’s been a very busy three months for us, as we transitioned back into living in Canada.  We’ve both been taking time off of YouTube to think about what kind of content we want to make in the future.  Do we still want to vlog?  Do we still want to talk about food and travel?  

We’re not too sure, and especially with our move back to Canada, where we can be closer to family and friends, we haven’t had much time to be as creative as we usually are.  Our focus first and foremost is taking care of our wellbeing, which we’ve been neglecting for a long time.  We have more support here and more options.  

And so, while we explore those options, and figure out what our next steps in life are, allow me to introduce you to the newest member of the Stawski family: Fudgy, the very sweet golden retriever puppy.  He’s been a huge help for me (Simon here) during this time, and I hope some of his cuteness brightens your day the way he’s brightened mine.

I’d like to just post some videos of Fudgy being cute and silly for a while.  I’ll be sharing some pics of him too, because I’m a fawning father alright?  He’s just so adorable ❤️

#goldenretriever #puppy #omgheissocuteamiright?

🌐 Website: https://www.ianwright8.com

The Official YouTube channel of ex Crystal Palace, Arsenal & England striker Ian Wright. 

From growing up in South London to the multiple unsuccessful trials and plans to give up playing, I signed my first professional contract with Crystal Palace a few months before my 22nd birthday. In 1991 I signed for Arsenal Football Club where I scored 185 goals in 288 appearances.  I went on to play 581 league games, scoring 387 goals for seven clubs in England and Scotland, earning 33 caps for the English national team. 

I am now fortunate enough to have a football broadcast career working for the BBC & ITV. 

Some Career Achievements:
185 goals in 288 appearances for Arsenal (2nd all time leading goal scorer)
117 goals in 253 starts for Crystal Palace (leading post war goal scorer)
33 caps for England Men’s National Team
Premier League Winner (Arsenal): 97/98
Premier League Golden Boot (Arsenal): 91/92
FA Cup (Arsenal) : 92/93, 97/98
European Cup Winners' Cup (Arsenal): 93/94

►剧情简介：
    　因为家庭变故，三个没有血缘关系的小孩成为了彼此新的家人。青梅竹马一起长大的三兄妹，一同经历，相互扶持，不因来时坎坷而沮丧，也不因前路漫漫而退缩。然而，原生家庭造成的心理问题如影随形，他们谒望被爱，却更加害怕失去。而曾经伤害过他们的人也再次闯入，打着家人的旗号想把他们分开。 
　　一边是彼此认定相互珍惜的新家人，一边是无法选择关系谈漠的亲生父母，他们艰难抉择却还是顾此失彼。他们不想新家人受到伤害，也不想人生被拖向深渊。 
　　面对两难的境遇，他们勇敢面对， 也努力让父母直面了自己的问题。在不同关系的爱中， 他们教会了自己成长，明晰了自己的内心一唯有直面原生家庭的影响，以家人之名相互治愈，才能清醒无畏的走下去， 成为更好的自己。

主演: 谭松韵 / 宋威龙 / 张新成 / 涂松岩 / 孙铱 / 何瑞贤 / 安戈
类型: 剧情 / 家庭
制片国家/地区: 中国大陆
语言: 汉语普通话
首播: 2020-08-10(中国大陆)
集数: 40

►剧情简介：
    　因为家庭变故，三个没有血缘关系的小孩成为了彼此新的家人。青梅竹马一起长大的三兄妹，一同经历，相互扶持，不因来时坎坷而沮丧，也不因前路漫漫而退缩。然而，原生家庭造成的心理问题如影随形，他们谒望被爱，却更加害怕失去。而曾经伤害过他们的人也再次闯入，打着家人的旗号想把他们分开。 
　　一边是彼此认定相互珍惜的新家人，一边是无法选择关系谈漠的亲生父母，他们艰难抉择却还是顾此失彼。他们不想新家人受到伤害，也不想人生被拖向深渊。 
　　面对两难的境遇，他们勇敢面对， 也努力让父母直面了自己的问题。在不同关系的爱中， 他们教会了自己成长，明晰了自己的内心一唯有直面原生家庭的影响，以家人之名相互治愈，才能清醒无畏的走下去， 成为更好的自己。

    　因为家庭变故，三个没有血缘关系的小孩成为了彼此新的家人。青梅竹马一起长大的三兄妹，一同经历，相互扶持，不因来时坎坷而沮丧，也不因前路漫漫而退缩。然而，原生家庭造成的心理问题如影随形，他们谒望被爱，却更加害怕失去。而曾经伤害过他们的人也再次闯入，打着家人的旗号想把他们分开。 
　　一边是彼此认定相互珍惜的新家人，一边是无法选择关系谈漠的亲生父母，他们艰难抉择却还是顾此失彼。他们不想新家人受到伤害，也不想人生被拖向深渊。 
　　面对两难的境遇，他们勇敢面对， 也努力让父母直面了自己的问题。在不同关系的爱中， 他们教会了自己成长，明晰了自己的内心一唯有直面原生家庭的影响，以家人之名相互治愈，才能清醒无畏的走下去， 成为更好的自己。

snippet.title: Ghost Stories From Our Childhood?! | The Thirsty Sisters #23
snippet.description:
Listen to us on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/show/5yx8txjfb7dMkosumEv6lQ?si=5Ew1dv6wRlCayZ0TQfo-Ug

Have you ever felt someone watching you from behind?! Well, we sure did!

On this week's lunar 7th month episode, The Thirsty Sisters have a special guest - Dee Kosh from Power 98FM, who brings to us his paranormal encounters from growing up in the Philippines. snippet.title: Lesti - Kulepas Dengan Ikhlas | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Lesti - Kulepas Dengan Ikhlas | Official Music Video

#Lesti #LestiBillar #MusicVideo #Lagubarulesti #laguadibal #videodangdutterbaru

Selepas merilis lagu bertemakan patah hati yang mendalam beberapa bulan lalu, kini Lesti kembali melahirkan sebuah karya baru dengan tema 'Keikhlasan'.  Dibawah naungan label rekaman 3D Entertainment dan manajemen artis STREAM Entertainment, single berjudul 'Kulepas Dengan Ikhlas' dirilis tepat dihari ulang tahun Lesti, 5 Agustus 2020, melalui music video di channel youtube 3D Entertainment.

Setelah sebelumnya kisah Lesti dikait-kaitkan dengan aktor Rizky Billar, yang memiliki background kisah cinta yang sama, dalam music video Lesti terbaru pun, keduanya dipertemukan. 

Adegan dalam music video tersebut sangat berkaitan dengan lirik yang diciptakan Adibal, penuh keikhlasan. Berangkat dari rasa simpati yang mendalam dan kedekatan secara pribadi, secara khusus Adibal Sahrul menciptakan lagu untuk Lesti.  "Lagu ini saya tulis tepat tanggal 17 Juli saat melihat postingan Lesti menghadiri pernikahan Rizky DA, cukup cepat bikinnya 1 jam aja... mungkin karena saya cukup dekat dengan mereka berdua, jadi saya dapat meraba apa yang mungkin mereka rasakan, khususnya Lesti, Kesan saya , lesti itu punya hati yg kuat ,apapun alasannya , gak mudah pastinya berada dalam situasi itu," tutur Adibal.

Lagu ini terasa paket lengkap dari sisi lirik, balutan musik yang menyentuh hati dan diperankan langsung oleh sosok yang mengalami kisahnya dan sebuah music video.  Semoga pesan besar dalam lagu ini dapat tersampaikan yaitu kita boleh merencanakan apa saja, pada akhirnya Tuhan yang menentukan.

#Lesti #LestiBillar #MusicVideo #Lagubarulesti #laguadibal #videodangdutterbaru

Selepas merilis lagu bertemakan patah hati yang mendalam beberapa bulan lalu, kini Lesti kembali melahirkan sebuah karya baru dengan tema 'Keikhlasan'.  Dibawah naungan label rekaman 3D Entertainment dan manajemen artis STREAM Entertainment, single berjudul 'Kulepas Dengan Ikhlas' dirilis tepat dihari ulang tahun Lesti, 5 Agustus 2020, melalui music video di channel youtube 3D Entertainment.

Setelah sebelumnya kisah Lesti dikait-kaitkan dengan aktor Rizky Billar, yang memiliki background kisah cinta yang sama, dalam music video Lesti terbaru pun, keduanya dipertemukan. 

Adegan dalam music video tersebut sangat berkaitan dengan lirik yang diciptakan Adibal, penuh keikhlasan. Berangkat dari rasa simpati yang mendalam dan kedekatan secara pribadi, secara khusus Adibal Sahrul menciptakan lagu untuk Lesti.  "Lagu ini saya tulis tepat tanggal 17 Juli saat melihat postingan Lesti menghadiri pernikahan Rizky DA, cukup cepat bikinnya 1 jam aja... mungkin karena saya cukup dekat dengan mereka berdua, jadi saya dapat meraba apa yang mungkin mereka rasakan, khususnya Lesti, Kesan saya , lesti itu punya hati yg kuat ,apapun alasannya , gak mudah pastinya berada dalam situasi itu," tutur Adibal.

Lagu ini terasa paket lengkap dari sisi lirik, balutan musik yang menyentuh hati dan diperankan langsung oleh sosok yang mengalami kisahnya dan sebuah music video.  Semoga pesan besar dalam lagu ini dapat tersampaikan yaitu kita boleh merencanakan apa saja, pada akhirnya Tuhan yang menentukan.

snippet.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《無濾鏡 No Filter》 (ft. 藤原浩 Hiroshi Fujiwara) Official Music Video
snippet.description:
林俊傑 x 舒淇
無需濾鏡 無法忽視的美麗

MV邀請國際級巨星—舒淇擔任女主角。透過天王天后級御用導演黃中平的導演視角，將〈無濾鏡〉令人沈醉夢幻的氛圍詮釋的十分到位，鏡頭更輕柔刻劃出舒淇的一舉一動，將「美」描繪得淋漓盡致。
_
林俊傑 JJ Lin 2020 美麗新作《無濾鏡》feat.藤原浩 Hiroshi Fujiwara
數位收聽  🎧 https://jjlin.lnk.to/NoFilterAY
_
眼眶中的妳 令人定神聚焦
指尖上的妳 令人怦然心跳

空氣因妳而芬芳瀰漫
緩著呼吸 輕輕屏息
深怕一不小心
破壞了眼前的美麗

離得越遠 越是著迷
輕觸心房 卻是如此黏膩
緊貼得無法呼吸
幾近忘記了存在的意義

就像被世界所有光芒愛戴著
成為失重的靈魂
祈求此刻化為永恆

無法定義 無所不在
無盡承載著 無需濾鏡
無法忽視的美麗
_
身兼創作歌王與潮牌創辦人 JJ林俊傑 神級跨界合作
攜手 國際潮流大師 藤原浩 打造最透徹的時尚單曲《無濾鏡》

原曲由藤原浩開啟並力邀JJ 共同創作，沈靜且步調優雅的節奏搭配上JJ迷幻慵懶的嗓音，綿密的情感溫柔地牽引著。

歌曲結合 Shoegazing 瞪鞋搖滾與 Dream Pop 夢幻流行樂，瀰漫著夢幻且令人陶醉的氛圍。透過懷秋的詞，緩緩步入歌曲的視角，沈醉在愛戀的芬芳氣息，無法自拔的著迷，音樂與歌詞巧妙地結合成一場失去引力的低速旅行

_
《無濾鏡》
曲：林俊傑/ 藤原浩
詞：張懷秋

“No Filter”
Composed by: JJ Lin /  Hiroshi Fujiwara 
Lyrics by: Harry Chang

褐⾊的神秘 盈盈在搖曳
A mystical presence, swaying elegantly
深邃的軌跡 宇宙間旅⾏
A profound existence in the universe
盤旋的髮髻 散發著茉莉
The lingering scent of jasmine in your hair
沈迷沈溺沈醉於妳
I am addicted, absorbed and lost in you

微微沿著肌膚紋理
Caressing your face
輕柔慢捻妳的淚滴
I gently wipe your tears away

妳就是那⽚最美的⾵景
You are the scenic portrait of allure
閉著眼腦海裡的對焦都是妳
The focus of my mind whenever I close my eyes
真實的不需向誰說明
Absolute and inexplicable
悄悄的把妳藏匿
You are the secret i want to keep

憂傷佈滿妳的氣息
The air of melancholy in you
飄⼊⼼海泛起漣漪
Stirs up ripples in my heart
微微沿著肌膚紋理
I caress the lines on your skin
輕柔慢捻妳的淚滴
And gently wipe your tears away
Girl, 褐⾊的神秘 盈盈在搖曳
Girl, your mystical presence, swaying elegantly
深邃的軌跡 宇宙間旅⾏
A profound existence in the universe
盤旋的髮髻 散發著茉莉
The lingering scent of jasmine in your hair
讓時間暫停 緊緊擁抱妳
Let time stand still, as I embrace you

妳就是那⽚最美的⾵景
You are the scenic portrait of allure
閉著眼腦海裡的對焦都是妳
The focus of my mind whenever I close my eyes
真實的不需向誰說明
Absolute and inexplicable
這瞬眼沒得編輯
This instant can’t be edited
美麗不需要濾鏡
Your beauty needs no ﬁlter
_

snippet.title: The Devil All The Time starring Tom Holland & Robert Pattinson | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Some people are just born to be buried. 

In Knockemstiff, Ohio and its neighboring backwoods, sinister characters — an unholy preacher (Robert Pattinson), twisted couple (Jason Clarke and Riley Keough), and crooked sheriff (Sebastian Stan) — converge around young Arvin Russell (Tom Holland) as he fights the evil forces that threaten him and his family. Spanning the time between World War II and the Vietnam war, director Antonio Campos’ THE DEVIL ALL THE TIME renders a seductive and horrific landscape that pits the just against the corrupted. Co-starring Bill Skarsgård, Mia Wasikowska, Harry Melling, Haley Bennett, and Pokey LaFarge, this suspenseful, finely-woven tale is adapted from Donald Ray Pollock's award-winning novel.

Watch The Devil All The Time at https://netflix.com/thedevilallthetime

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is the world's leading streaming entertainment service with 193 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, documentaries and feature films across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can watch as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, on any internet-connected screen. Members can play, pause and resume watching, all without commercials or commitments.

Mat and Yianni are at it again, and they're going head-to-head in another epic drag race... In the wet! This time, Mat's actually in the car with the least power! Although his M8 Competition is still hiding a 4.4-litre twin-turbo V8 under the bonnet that will produce 625hp and 750Nm of torque! As for the GT-R and Porsche 911 Turbo S? snippet.description:
▶️ Intérprete: Julliany Souza  
▶️ Compositores: Ana Paula Valadão 

LETRA:

Preciso de Ti 
Preciso do Teu perdão 
Preciso de Ti
Quebranta meu coração 
Como a corsa 
Anseia por águas 
Assim tenho sede 
Como terra seca 
Assim é minh’alma 
Preciso de Ti 

Distante de Ti Senhor 
Não posso viver 
Não vale a pena existir 
Escuta o meu clamor 
Mais que o ar que eu respiro 
Preciso de Ti 

Não posso esquecer 
O que fizestes por mim 
Como alto o céu 
Tua misericórdia é sem fim 
Como um pai 
Se compadece dos filhos 
Assim Tu me amas 
Afasta as minhas transgressões 
Preciso de Ti 

Distante de Ti Senhor
Não posso viver 
Não vale a pena existir 
Escuta o meu clamor 
Mais que o ar que eu respiro 
Preciso de Ti 

E as lutas vem tentando me afastar de Ti 
Frieza e escuridão procuram me cegar 
Mas, eu não vou desistir 
Ajuda-me, Senhor 
Eu quero permanecer 
Contigo até o fim

snippet.title: Alok feat. MC Caverinha - Calça Angelical
snippet.description:
Spotify https://bit.ly/alokspotify
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/livealok/
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/alokgamechanger/
Twitter https://twitter.com/alokoficial


Letra: 

Ok, prazer, Caverinha 
Mais conhecido como Mestre 

É que eu já 
Passei no teste 

Se tu quiser peitar 
A minha guilda 
“Cê” já sabe o que acontece 

É capa 
Gasta gelo, não consegue 
É capa 

Em bermuda se moscou, é capa 
Purgatório se moscou, é capa 
Mano, é capa

É, na moral, pego todo Loot do seu quintal 
Quando eu passo, ela paga pau
Tô chavezin de calça angelical 

Eu rusho de 12 (yeah)
Não adianta “vim” gastar gelo 
“Cê” não escapa, nem se for a Frozen (yeah, yeah, yeah)

Pulou em cima da Factory 
Acho que isso é medo de mim 
Ninguém me peita, todo mundo corre 
Eu sou o terror do Zé Carrin 

Se um cai, a gente já socorre 
Nenhum dos meus “fica” pra trás (2x) (yeah, yeah, yeah)

É, na moral, pego todo Loot do seu quintal
Quando eu passo, ela paga pau 

Tô chavezin de calça angelical 
Da hora, legal 

É, na moral, pego todo Loot do seu quintal
Quando eu passo, ela paga pau 

Tô chavezin de calça angelical 

Eu faço hit free 
Ainda taco fire nessa cena 
Elas me “pede” codiguin 
Acha que eu sou dono da Garena
 
Ela pede umas “skin”
Falo “não”, elas me acham ignorante 
Te mando até uns presentin 
E faço você virar diamante 

Hoje eu tô blindado 
De colete 4 
Squad formado 
Nem o gás me pega 

Eu tô equipado 
Fortemente armado 
Se eu pego AWM, pra esses campers já azeda 

Veio de hack 
Minha mina explodiu 
Esse cara é boot, como pode?
Zerei a sala com mais de 10 kill 
Tá na hora de voltar pro lobby

É, na moral, pego todo Loot do seu quintal
Quando eu passo, ela paga pau 

Tô chavezin de calça angelical 
Da hora, legal

É, na moral, pego todo Loot do seu quintal
Quando eu passo, ela paga pau 

Tô chavezin de calça angelical 
Da hora, legal

snippet.description:
AR POLAR ALCANÇARÁ METADE DO BRASIL COM CHANCE DE NEVE

A MetSul Meteorologia adverte para uma massa de ar polar enorme e muito intensa que vai atingir praticamente a metade do território brasileiro e grande parte da América do Sul nesta semana com potencial de ser um evento histórico de frio e neve. Verdadeira bolha de ar antártico avançará pela Argentina e vai atingir pela sua trajetória continental o Sul, o Centro-Oeste, o Sudeste e parte do Norte do Brasil. 

——

Assine a MetSul Meteorologia e tenha acesso a conteúdos exclusivos, análises dos nossos meteorologistas e uma plataforma de dados com previsões para todo o Brasil de horas, dias, semanas e meses. É muito mais informação para o seu planejamento. 

Site e assinaturas: www.metsul.co
Twitter: @metsul

snippet.title: Bayern-Tornado fegt über Barca hinweg: FC Barcelona - FC Bayern 2:8 | UEFA Champions League | DAZN
snippet.description:
Im Viertelfinale der Champions League kommt es zum vorgezogenen Finale zwischen dem FC Barcelona und dem FC Bayern München. Thomas Müller trifft nach vier Minuten zum 1:0 für die Münchner, David Alaba gleicht nur wenig später per Eigentor aus. Nach einer halben Stunde folgt innerhalb von ca. zehn Minuten ein Dreierpack der Bayern durch Perisic, Gnabry und Müller zum 4:1 Pausenstand. Nach dem Seitenwechsel verkürzt zunächst Luis Suarez auf 2:4, ehe Bayerns Tormaschinerie nochmal Fahrt aufnimmt. Kimmich, Lewandowski und ein Doppelpack Coutinhos schrauben das Ergebnis auf 8:2 für den deutschen Double-Sieger, die damit ins Halbfinale der Champions League einziehen.

Nach dem Seitenwechsel verkürzt zunächst Luis Suarez auf 2:4, ehe Bayerns Tormaschinerie nochmal Fahrt aufnimmt. Kimmich, Lewandowski und ein Doppelpack Coutinhos schrauben das Ergebnis auf 8:2 für den deutschen Double-Sieger, die damit ins Halbfinale der Champions League einziehen.

snippet.title: De Jong schießt Sevilla zum 6. Mal ins Finale: FC Sevilla - ManU 2:1 | UEFA Europa League | DAZN
snippet.description:
Der FC Sevilla steht erneut im Finale der UEFA Europa League. Anfangs standen die Zeichen dafür nicht sonderlich gut. Nach einem Foul an Rashford verwandelte Bruno Fernandes in der 9. Minute den darauf folgenden Elfmeter zum 1:0. Die Blancirojos ließen sich nicht aus der Ruhe bringen und konnten in der 26. Minute durch Suso ausgleichen. Obwohl United viele Chancen hatte, zeigte Sevilla, warum ihnen der Wettbewerb liegt. In der 77 Minute nutzte der Ex-Gladbacher Luuk de Jong eine Unsicherheit in der Hintermannschaft kaltschnäuzig aus. Sevilla steht damit zum 6. Mal im Finale der UEFA Europa League.

snippet.title: Überraschung! Joker Dembele löst Bayern-Ticket: Man City - Lyon 1:3 | UEFA Champions League | DAZN
snippet.description:
In Halbzeit eins liegt die Überraschung bereits in der Luft: Lyon geht in der 24. Minute durch Maxwel Cornet in Führung und lässt den Favoriten aus Manchester nicht wirklich ins Spiel finden. ManCity kommt jedoch besser aus der Pause und gleicht in der 69. Minute durch Kevin de Bruyne verdient zum 1:1 aus. Der frisch eingewechselte Moussa Dembele lässt OLs Hoffnungen auf das Halbfinale erneut aufleben als er in der 79. Minute zur erneuten Führung trifft und setzt in der 89. Minute mit dem 1:3 den Deckel drauf. Olympique Lyon qualifiziert sich überraschend für das Halbfinale und trifft am Mittwoch auf den FC Bayern München.

snippet.title: Matthias im Porsche Entwicklungs-Zentrum I GRIP
snippet.description:
Exklusiv und bislang noch keinem TV-Team der Welt erlaubt: GRIP darf einen geheimen Prototyp der Superklasse testen! Die Rede ist vom neuen Porsche Panamera! GRIP-Testfahrer Matthias Malmedie ist dafür unterwegs nach Weissach ins Porsche-Entwicklungszentrum, wo er das automobile Heiligtum betreten darf. Der Clou: Matthias darf den Panamera nicht nur für die Zuschauer testen, sondern muss Porsche auch bei der Entwicklung helfen! Exklusiv für GRIP wirft Matthias einen Blick hinter die Kulissen der Porsche-Entwickler: Wie arbeiten Testfahrer? Wie funktioniert die Geheimhaltung? Und: Wie fährt sich der neue Porsche überhaupt? Denn Matthias bekommt auch noch den Schlüssel zum getarnten Testauto, dem Porsche Panamera Erlkönig, überreicht… 

Abonnieren unseren Kanal: https://www.youtube.com/user/GRIPRTL2?sub_confirmation=1 
Komplette Folgen GRIP auf TV NOW: http://www.tvnow.de/rtl2/grip-das-motormagazin
Alle Infos zur Sendung: http://www.rtl2.de/sendung/grip-das-motormagazin

GRIP bei Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/grip
GRIP bei YouTube abonnieren: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=GRIPRTL2

Seit 2007 bietet „GRIP - Das Motormagazin“ seinen Zuschauern sonntags bei RTLZWEI kompetenten Motorjournalismus vereint mit Tests der Superlative. Mit viel Humor, einem hochwertigen Look und außergewöhnlichen Themen verbindet „GRIP - Das Motormagazin“ Unterhaltung rund um die Motorwelt mit Service für den Verbraucher.

Die Moderatoren Det Müller, Matthias Malmedie, Helge Thomsen, Cyndie Allemann und Niki Schelle zeigen jede Woche die heißesten Auto-Trends, wagen rasante Versuche und geben kompetente Tipps.

GRIP ist aber nicht nur im TV zu finden. So gibt es ein Printmagazin, das in der DAZ-Verlagsgruppe erscheint, Musik-Compilations in Kooperation mit Sony Music und Events wie das „GRIP - Das Motorevent“. Auch bei Youtube, Facebook und Instagram begeistert GRIP durch regelmäßig aktualisierte Inhalte die Abonnenten.

"GRIP - Das Motormagazin", immer sonntags im TV bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: Zwetschgenkuchen ohne Teig anrühren, einfach lecker 🍰👌
snippet.description:
Hallo ihr Lieben 🔆
Heute bereite ich einen Zwetschgenkuchen zu, der
ohne viel Aufwand gezaubert ist, denn der Teig muss 
nicht extra angerührt werden. Probiert ihn mal aus ;)

Ich freu mich schon über eure nachgemacht Bilder auf:  📸 https://www.instagram.com/reniasbackwelt/?hl=de

Das sind die Zutaten:

240g        Mehl
240g        Weichweizengries
180g        Zucker
2Tl           Backpulver
200g        Butter (kalt)

1000g      Zwetschgen
2Tl           Zimt

Backrahmen 19x27cm oder 26 Springform

Bei 180° Ober-Unterhitze ca 60 Minuten backen

Viel Spaß beim ausprobieren :)

     (http://prozis.com/3Tv6)

_______

✘ Folgt mir, Freunde!
➞ Instagram: sascha_huber_official

________

✘ Hühnerfilet mit Kürbiskernkruste, Parmesansoße und Süßkartoffel Wedges (2-3 Personen)

✘ Zutaten 
➞ 150-200g Cocktailtomaten 
➞ 2-3 Süßkartoffeln (Kartoffeln) 
➞ 1-2 EL Olivenöl
➞ 1 kleine-mittlere Zwiebel 
➞ 2 Knoblauchzehen
➞ 200ml Wasser
➞ Suppenpulver (Suppenwürfel) für die Gemüsebrühe
➞ 300-500g Hühnerfilet (Hähnchenbrust)
➞ 50-80g Parmesan 
➞ 50-100g Kürbiskerne - grob gehackt oder selbst zerkleinern (http://prozis.com/5Cjj)
➞ 6 getrocknete Tomate 
➞ 150-200g Frischkäse
➞ Salz, Pfeffer, Oregano, Paprikapulver

(Alternative: Soße mit Linsennudeln oder Kichererbsennudeln gönnen: http://prozis.com/5CjH)

➞ Küchenwaage ohne Batterie: (http://prozis.com/4qYN)

✘ Zubereitung

Backofen auf 200° Ober-/Unterhitze vorheizen. 150-200g Cocktailtomaten in einen Topf mit heißem Wasser geben und bei mittlerer Hitze ca. 10 Minuten köcheln lassen. (Küchenwaage ohne Batterie: http://prozis.com/4qYN)

2-3 Süßkartoffeln in Spalten schneiden. Dann in einer großen Schüssel mit 1-2 EL Öl, etwas Salz, Pfeffer, Oregano und Paprikapulver vermengen. Die Süßkartoffeln auf einem mit Backpapier belegten Backblech verteilen und 25-30 Minuten goldbraun backen.  Etwas Platz für das Fleisch lassen.  

1 kleine-mittlere Zwiebel und 2 Knoblauchzehen schälen und würfeln. 200ml heißes Wasser in einem Topf zum Köcheln bringen und für die Gemüsebrühe das Suppenpulver (Würfel) hinzugeben.

500g Hähnchenfilet mit Salz, Pfeffer und Paprikapulver von beiden Seiten würzen. In einer Pfanne etwas Olivenöl erhitzen und die Hähnchen in der Pfanne 3-5 Minuten scharf anbraten bis sie außen goldbraun sind. 1 Seite danach mit Parmesan, gehackten Kürbiskernen und nochmal mit Parmesan bestreuen und in den letzten 12-15 Minuten der Kartoffel Backzeit die Hähnchen mit auf das Blech geben und mitbacken, bis das Fleisch innen nur noch ganz leicht rosa ist. 

Für die Soße die Cocktailtomaten schälen. Knoblauch und Zwiebel bei mittlerer Hitze in der Pfanne 1-2 Minuten glasig dünsten. Anschließend die getrockneten Tomaten klein schneiden und in die Pfanne geben. Nun die Cocktailtomaten vierteln und mit in die Pfanne geben. Das Ganze mit der Gemüsebrühe ablöschen und kurz aufkochen lassen. Unter Rühren den Frischkäse in die Pfanne geben und nachdem sich der Frischkäse in der Soße aufgelöst hat, den Parmesan dazugeben und ebenfalls unterrühren. Mit Pfeffer, Salz und Paprikapulver abschmecken und genießen. Mahlzeit, Freunde.

✘ Nährwerte (2-3 Personen)

Eiweiß: 189g
Kohlenhydrate: 85g

snippet.title: Meet Rampart – Apex Legends Character Trailer
snippet.description:
The best modder in the Outlands, Rampart backs up her big mouth with big guns she designed herself. http://x.ea.com/63058

When one door burns to the ground, another opens. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh lost her shop, but she gained an invite to the Apex Games. She may not have set out to become a Legend, but now that she’s here, she’s excited to show the world what Sheila can do. 


Rampart can’t go home, so she’s going big -- her natural affinity for LMGs allows her to shoot more and reload faster. She can drop a high-tech cover to block incoming shots and joice up her team’s fire. And when you really need to call in the big guns, her Ultimate does just that. When you meet Sheila, you better hope she’s on your side.

Ready to dance?

Learn more about Rampart’s story: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M9Pmf9AB4Mo

localizations.ko.description:
아웃랜드의 최고 제조의 달인인 램파트는 과장된 표현을 좋아합니다. 그리고 그 표현을 자신이 직접 디자인한 커다란 총을 들고 증명해내죠. http://x.ea.com/63058

문이 닫히면 어딘가 창문이 열리기 마련입니다. 람야 ""램파트"" 파레크는 자신의 가게를 잃었지만, Apex 게임의 초대장을 받았습니다. 램파트는 처음부터 레전드가 되기로 마음먹은 건 아니지만, Apex 게임에 도착한 이상 쉴라의 파괴적인 능력을 세상에 보여주려 합니다. 


돌아갈 집이 없는 램파트는 오히려 대담한 도전장을 던집니다. 램파트는 LMG를 능숙하게 다루어 더 많이 쏘고 더 빠르게 재장전을 합니다. 최첨단 엄폐물을 배치하여 들어오는 총격을 막고 팀의 총격을 강화합니다. 그러다 정말로 큰 총을 불러야 할 때가 온다면, 그녀는 얼티밋 스킬을 꺼내듭니다. 쉴라를 만나게 된다면, 반드시 램파트가 팀에 있길 바랍니다.

함께 춤추실 준비 되셨습니까?

localizations.sv.description:
Rampart är den bästa moddaren i Outlands och hon blandar mycket snack och mycket verkstad tack vare vapnen hon själv har designat. http://x.ea.com/63058

När en dörr brinner ner till grunden öppnas en annan. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh förlorade sin butik, men hon fick en inbjudan till Apex Games. Hon siktade kanske inte på att bli en legend, men nu när hon är här ser hon fram emot att visa världen vad Sheila går för.


Rampart kan inte gå hem, så hon går all-in --  hennes naturliga förkärlek för LMG låter henne skjuta mer och ladda om snabbare. Hon kan ta fram ett högteknologiskt skydd som blockerar inkommande skott och sätter piff på sitt lags ammunition. Och när det verkligen blir dags för det tunga artilleriet, så kan du förvänta dig just det från hennes Ultimate. När du träffar Sheila får du hoppas att hon är på din sida.

Redo att dansa?

localizations.it.title: Rampart – Apex Legends - Il trailer
localizations.it.description:
Rampart è la regina della tecnologia nelle Terre Straniere. Grazie alle armi da fuoco che progetta e costruisce, non ha paura di mostrare ai nemici di che pasta è fatta. http://x.ea.com/63058

Quando si chiude una porta, si apre un portone. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh ha perso il suo negozio, ma ha ricevuto un invito per gli Apex Games. Non avrebbe mai creduto che un giorno sarebbe diventata una leggenda, ma ora è impaziente di mettersi al lavoro e mostrare al mondo intero di cosa è capace Sheila. 


Rampart non può tornare a casa, perciò è pronta a dare il massimo nell'arena. Il suo talento naturale con le LMG le consente di sparare più a lungo e ricaricare più rapidamente. Inoltre, può posizionare una copertura hi-tech che blocca i colpi in arrivo e potenzia quelli in uscita. La sua mitragliatrice, poi, è perfetta per affrontare le situazioni più difficili in battaglia. Quando incontrerai Sheila, spera che sia dalla tua parte.

Preparati a entrare in pista!

localizations.no.description:
Den beste modderen i randen, Rampart, forsvarer den store kjeften sin med de store våpnene hun selv har utviklet. http://x.ea.com/63058

Når én dør blir til aske, er det en annen som åpnes. Ramya «Rampart» Parekh mistet verkstedet sitt, men hun fikk en invitasjon til Apex-lekene. Hun hadde kanskje ingen planer om å bli til en legende, men nå er hun her og hun gleder seg til å vise verden hva Sheila kan gjøre. 


Rampart kan ikke dra hjem, så da retter hun kursen mot seier – hennes naturlige preferanse for LMG-er lar henne skyte mer og lade om raskere. Hun kan sette ut et avansert skydd som blokkerer skudd fra fienden og piffer opp ildkraften til laget sitt. Og når situasjonen virkelig krever kraftigere skytevåpen, så fikser ultimaten hennes akkurat det. Når du endelig får hilse på Sheila bør du håpe på at hun er på din side.

localizations.ru.title: Встречайте Рампарт — трейлер персонажа Apex Legends
localizations.ru.description:
За хвастовством Рампарт, автора лучших модификаций во Внешних землях, стоят здоровенные пушки, конструкцию которых она продумала сама. http://x.ea.com/63058

Когда одна дверь сгорает дотла, открывается другая. Рамья «Рампарт» Парекх лишилась магазина, но обрела приглашение на Игры Apex. Может, она и не планировала становиться легендой, но раз уж она здесь, то с радостью продемонстрирует всему миру, на что способна Шейла. 


У Рампарт нет пути назад, поэтому она гордо шагает вперед с пушкой наперевес. Благодаря своей тяге к ручным пулеметам она может перезаряжать их быстрее и делать больше выстрелов. Ее примочки обеспечивают отряду надежное укрытие, которое блокирует огонь снаружи и усиливает стрельбу команды. Если же нужно пустить в ход тяжелую артиллерию, ее спецумение придется весьма кстати. Повстречаетесь с Шейлой — надейтесь, что она на вашей стороне.

localizations.es-MX.title: Conoce a Rampart – Tráiler de personaje de Apex Legends
localizations.es-MX.description:
Rampart es la mejor modificadora de las tierras desconocidas y, aunque habla demasiado, respalda sus palabras con grandes armas que diseñó ella misma. http://x.ea.com/63058

Cuando se quema una puerta, otra se abre. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh perdió su tienda, pero ganó una invitación a los Apex Games. Quizás nunca buscó ser una leyenda, pero ahora que está aquí, podrá mostrarle al mundo lo que Sheila puede hacer. 


Rampart no puede regresar a casa, así que irá con todo: su afinidad natural por las ametralladoras ligeras le permite disparar más y recargar más rápido. Puede desplegar coberturas de alta tecnología para bloquear los disparos enemigos y amplificar los de su equipo. Y cuando realmente necesites un peso pesado, su habilidad definitiva es lo que buscas. Cuando conozcas a Sheila, desearás que esté de tu parte.

localizations.fr-FR.title: Découvrez Rampart - Trailer personnage Apex Legends
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Meilleure experte en modding des Terres Sauvages, Rampart a le verbe haut et le canon - qu’elle a souvent conçu elle-même - à portée de main. http://x.ea.com/63058

Quand une porte brûle, une autre s’ouvre. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh a perdu sa boutique, mais elle a gagné une invitation aux Jeux Apex. Rampart n’était pas programmée pour devenir une Légende mais, maintenant qu’elle est dans la place, elle compte bien montrer de quoi Sheila est capable. 


Rampart ne peut pas rentrer chez elle, alors autant sortir le grand jeu : son attirance naturelle pour les mitrailleuses lui confère une cadence de tir élevée et un rechargement rapide. Elle a aussi recours à une couverture technologique qui bloque les tirs ennemis et amplifie ceux de son équipe. Et, pour ce qui est d‘envoyer du lourd, sa capacité ultime fait largement le boulot : si vous croisez Sheila, priez pour être dans son camp !

Vous êtes prêts à danser ?

localizations.pl.title: Poznaj Rampart – zwiastun postaci Apex Legends
localizations.pl.description:
Rampart to najlepsza moderka na Odludziu. Jest wyszczekana i ma własnoręcznie zaprojektowane potężne spluwy. http://x.ea.com/63058

Gdy jedne drzwi spłoną, otworzą się następne. Ramya „Rampart” Parekh straciła swój sklep, ale otrzymała zaproszenie do Igrzysk Apex. Może i nie miała w planach zostać legendą, ale gdy już się tu znalazła, z radością pokaże światu, co potrafi jej Sheila. 


Rampart nie może wrócić do domu, więc idzie na całego – jej naturalna ciągota do LKM-ów sprawia, że jest bardziej wydajną strzelczynią oraz szybko przeładowuje bronie. Potrafi postawić zaawansowaną technologicznie osłonę blokującą nadlatujące pociski i zmotywować swoją drużynę. I kiedy naprawdę chcesz wytoczyć najcięższe działa, jej zdolność specjalna zrealizuje to w pełni. Gdy spotkasz Sheilę, módl się, żeby była po twojej stronie.

Gotowi do tańca?

localizations.ja.description:
アウトランズ随一のモッダーであるランパートは、自ら設計したビッグな銃でビッグマウスを体現してみせる。http://x.ea.com/63058

ドアが1枚焼け落ちれば、また1枚が開く。ラミャ・“ランパート”・パレクは店を失ったが、Apexゲームへの招待状を掴んだ。レジェンドを目指すつもりはないかもしれないが、やって来たからにはシェイラの力量を世界に知らしめようと心躍らせている。


帰る家がないランパートは大胆に行く。LMGとの相性が良いため、弾数が多く、リロードが高速。ハイテクカバーで銃撃を受け止め、チームの火力を上げる。ビッグガンが必要になったときには、「アルティメット」の出番である。シェイラと会うときには、彼女が味方であることを願おう。

さあ、踊ろうか？

localizations.pt-BR.title: Conheça Rampart - Trailer de Personagem de Apex Legends
localizations.pt-BR.description:
A melhor modder das Terras Ermas, Rampart nunca para de falar, mas está sempre bem armada. http://x.ea.com/63058

Quando uma porta pega fogo e vira cinzas, outra se abre. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh perdeu a oficina que tinha, mas ganhou um convite para os Jogos Apex. Ela não desejava se tornar uma Lenda, mas agora que está aqui, ela quer mostrar para o mundo o que Sheila pode fazer. 


Rampart veio pra ficar, então ela aposta tudo na afinidade natural com metralhadoras leves, permitindo que dispare mais e recarregue mais rápido. Ela pode posicionar uma cobertura de alta tecnologia que bloqueia disparos inimigos e amplifica disparos aliados. E quando precisar de armamento pesado, a Suprema dela cumpre bem o serviço. Quando conhecer Sheila, torça para ela estar do seu lado.

Vamos dançar?

localizations.da.title: Mød Rampart – Karakter-trailer til Apex Legends
localizations.da.description:
Rampart en en rapkæftet modder fra Outlands, der selv designer sine egne våben. http://x.ea.com/63058

Når en dør går op i flammer, er det altid et vindue, der åbner sig. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh mistede sin butik, men til gengæld fik hun en invitation til Apex Games. Det var ikke hendes mål at blive en legende, men nu hvor hun er med i kampen, glæder hun sig til at vise, hvad Sheila kan. 


Rampart går ikke stille med dørene – hun har smag for maskingeværer og kan skyde og lade hurtigt. Hun kan smide en højteknologisk dækning, der beskytter hende mod fjendens skud, samtidig med at den forstærker hendes holdkammeraters skud. Og når du virkelig har brug for det tunge skyts, er hendes ultimate det perfekte valg. Når du ser Sheila, håber du straks, at hun er på dit hold.

Er du klar til at danse?

Få mere at vide om Ramparts historie: [link].

localizations.de-DE.title: Triff Rampart – Apex Legends Charakter-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Als beste Modderin der Outlands lässt Rampart ihren großen Sprüchen ebenso große Waffen folgen, die sie selbst entworfen hat. http://x.ea.com/63058

Wenn eine Tür niedergebrannt wird, öffnet sich eine andere. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh hat ihren Laden verloren, aber eine Einladung zu den Apex-Spielen erhalten. Sie hatte zwar nie vor, eine Legende zu werden, aber wo sie schon mal hier ist, freut sie sich darauf, der ganzen Welt zu zeigen, was Sheila kann. 


Da Rampart nicht nach Hause gehen kann, geht sie aufs Ganze. Dank ihrer Vorliebe für LMGs kann sie länger feuern und schneller nachladen. Außerdem kann sie Beschuss mit einer Hightech-Deckung blocken und die Schüsse ihres Teams verstärken. Und falls sie mal richtig schweres Gerät braucht, greift sie auf ihre ultimative Fähigkeit zurück. Wenn du Sheila triffst, solltest du hoffen, dass sie auf deiner Seite steht.

Bist du bereit für ein Tänzchen?

localizations.pt-PT.title: Fica a conhecer Rampart - Trailer de personagem de Apex Legends
localizations.pt-PT.description:
A melhor modder das Outlands, Rampart fala demais, mas as armas enormes que cria também são demais.
http://x.ea.com/63058


Quando uma porta se fecha, abre-se uma janela a tiro. Ramya ""Rampart"" Parekh pode ter perdido a sua oficina, mas ganhou um convite para os Apex Games. Nunca quis ser uma lenda mas, já que está aqui, vai mostrar ao mundo o poder de Sheila. 


Rampart não pode ir para casa, por isso vai dar tudo o que tem. A sua afinidade natural por LMGs dá-lhe uma velocidade de disparo maior e um tempo de recarga mais curto. Pode criar uma cobertura energética para bloquear o fogo inimigo e potenciar os disparos da sua equipa. E, quando precisares de uma arma mesmo grande, o seu Derradeiro não desilude. Quando vires a Sheila, vais rezar para que esteja na tua equipa.

Dançamos?

localizations.fi.title: Tutustu Rampartiin – Apex Legends -hahmotraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Outlandsin paras modaaja Rampart seisoo suurten puheidensa takana käyttämällä itse suunnittelemiaan isoja aseita. http://x.ea.com/63058
 
 Kun yksi ovi palaa maan tasalle, toinen avautuu. Ramya ”Rampart” Parekh menetti kauppansa mutta sai kutsun Apex Gamesiin. Hän ei ehkä pyrkinyt legendaksi, mutta nyt, kun hän on täällä, hän on innoissaan päästessään näyttämään maailmalle, mihin Sheila pystyy. 
 
 
 Rampart ei voi mennä kotiin, joten hän pistää kaiken peliin – hänen luonnollinen mieltymyksensä kevyisiin konekivääreihin antaa hänen ampua enemmän ja ladata nopeammin. Hän pystyy pystyttämään huipputeknisen suojan estämään kohti tulevat laukaukset ja tehostamaan ryhmänsä tulitusta. Kun sinun todella pitää saada suuret aseet taisteluun, hänen Ultimatensa tekee juuri sen. Kun tapaat Sheilan, sinun on paras toivoa, että hän on sinun puolellasi.
 
 Oletko valmis tanssiin?
 
 Lue lisää Rampartin tarinasta: [link].

localizations.nl-NL.title: Maak kennis met Rampart – Personage-trailer Apex Legends
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Rampart, de beste Modder in de Outlands, heeft een grote mond, maar maakt het ook waar met de grote wapens die ze zelf heeft ontworpen. http://x.ea.com/63058

Als één deur tot op de grond afbrandt, gaat er een andere deur open. Ramya “Rampart” Parekh is een winkel armer, maar een uitnodiging voor de Apex Games rijker. Ze was misschien niet van plan om een Legend te worden, maar nu ze hier is, wil ze de wereld graag laten zien wat Sheila kan. 


Rampart kan niet naar huis, dus ze pakt het groots aan: dankzij haar natuurlijke affiniteit voor LMG's kan ze meer schieten en sneller herladen. Ze kan hightech dekking geven om vijandelijke schoten te blokkeren en het vuur van haar team op te peppen. En als je echt grote wapens nodig hebt, doet haar Ultimate precies dat. Als je Sheila ontmoet, kun je maar beter hopen dat ze aan jouw kant staat.

Klaar om te dansen?

Ontdek meer over het verhaal van Rampart: [link].

localizations.zh-Hant.title: 見識蕾帕特 -《Apex 英雄》角色預告片
localizations.zh-Hant.description:
身為邊疆最厲害的模組師，蕾帕特雖然口氣不小，但她自己設計的槍枝也不賴。http://x.ea.com/63058

天無絕人之路。拉米雅‧帕里克，綽號「蕾帕特」，失去了她的商店，但她卻受邀參與 Apex 競賽。儘管她從未打算成為一名英雄，但她現在等不及想要讓全世界瞧瞧席拉的厲害


蕾帕特回不了家，所以她決定大幹一場－－她擅長使用輕機槍，這讓她能夠更常射擊並更快地填裝彈藥她能夠部署一道高科技掩護來阻擋來襲攻擊，同時強化隊友的彈藥當你需要使用強大的火力時，交給她的絕招當你見到席拉時，你最好希望它是你的隊友
